decorations_added: Transform this bedroom into a spooky Halloween scene with: fake cobwebs stretched across the teal walls and corners with large black spiders, hanging bats from the ceiling, a skeletal figure leaning against the wardrobe, jack-o'-lanterns and carved pumpkins on the floor near corners, orange and purple string lights draped across the walls, black silhouette decals of haunted trees and witches on the teal walls, scattered autumn leaves on the floor, spooky atmospheric purple and orange lighting creating eerie shadows, and a witch's hat and spell books placed on top of the wardrobe
